### Pet API Testing

### 1. Get all pets for a shelter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/pets/shelter/shelter-1
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get pet by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/pets/{{petId}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Create a new pet
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/pets/shelter/shelter-1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Buddy",
  "species": "Dog",
  "breed": "Golden Retriever",
  "age": 3,
  "gender": "Male",
  "description": "Friendly and energetic dog looking for a loving family.",
  "imageUrl": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552053831-71594a27632d?w=300&h=200&fit=crop&crop=faces"
}

### 4. Update pet status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/pets/{{petId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

"Available"

### 5. Delete pet
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/pets/{{petId}}

